    {id:10,category:"tax",categoryName:"税收优惠",categoryNameEn:"Tax Incentives",title:"展会境外展品进口和销售免税",titleEn:"Tax Exemption for Exhibition Imported Goods",summary:"对展会境外展品进口和销售，免征进口关税、进口环节增值税和消费税。",summaryEn:"Import duty, VAT and consumption tax exempted for imported and sold exhibition goods from overseas.",content:"对在海南举办的展会境外展品，进口和销售环节免征进口关税、进口环节增值税和消费税。展品可在展后留购或复运出境。",contentEn:"For overseas exhibition goods at exhibitions held in Hainan, import and sales are exempted from import duty, VAT and consumption tax. Goods can be purchased or re-exported after exhibition.",interpretation:"这项政策支持海南会展经济发展，降低展会成本，吸引更多国际展会落户海南。",interpretationEn:"This policy supports Hainan's MICE economy development, reduces exhibition costs and attracts more international exhibitions.",highlight:"展会境外展品免税，促进会展经济发展",highlightEn:"Tax-free exhibition goods, promoting MICE economy",link:"https://www.hnftp.gov.cn/zczdtx/hxzc/zhjwzp",relatedQuestions:[{zh:"哪些展会可以享受这个政策？",en:"Which exhibitions can enjoy this policy?"},{zh:"展品免税如何申请？",en:"How to apply for exhibition goods tax exemption?"},{zh:"展后可以留购吗？",en:"Can goods be purchased after exhibition?"},{zh:"展品销售有什么限制？",en:"Any restrictions on exhibition goods sales?"}]}
